      "rationale": "The pedicle screw and rod are represented as elastic-plastic continua with Ti-6Al-4V material properties from ASTM F136. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) captures screw-rod interface behavior. Model form is consistent with prior FDA-published spinal implant FEA guidance."
    },
