      "rationale": "Young's modulus, yield strength, and ultimate strength were taken from certified material test reports for the specific lot used in bench testing. CMM measurements confirmed screw diameter and rod diameter within 0.02 mm of nominal. Monte Carlo propagation showed QoI uncertainty < 3.5%."
    },
    {
