      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the clinical loading envelope including at least two load levels and two fixation configurations.",
      "rationale": "Testing was performed under a single ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration only. The required level of 3 demands multiple test conditions spanning the clinical envelope; only one condition was evaluated, yielding an achieved level of 2. This is the sole factor below required level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
