      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA boundary conditions reproduce ASTM F1717 fixture kinematics; applied displacement rate equivalent to quasi-static experimental rate.",
      "rationale": "The F1717 test fixture geometry and boundary conditions were replicated in the FEA model using rigid body constraints at the potting block interfaces. Displacement-controlled loading at 5 mm/min was reproduced quasi-statically. Equivalency confirmed by comparing reaction force at zero displacement to fixture pre-load measurements."
    },
    {
