      "rationale": "For all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm), E/uval ranged from 0.41 to 1.23, well below the 1.96 threshold. Percent differences between mean FEA and mean experimental were 2.1%, 4.7%, and 3.8% respectively, all within the 10% acceptance bound."
    },
